<dl id="un6017bl"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="un6" href="#un6017">UN6: </a>  <a href="../../FF/unbs/un6all.htm#un6017bl"> (NLI.4) 17(bl)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ hot paralysis kiss, <small>Red</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="un6017bl"><li>Ulysses </li><li><a href="../../ulex/t/lext.htm#un6017bl">2021</a> </li><li><a href="../../ulex/t/t86.htm#un6017bl">2017</a> </li><li><a href="../../ulex/t/t86.htm#un6017bl">1986 (18.106)</a> </li><li><a href="../../ulex/t/l22t.htm#un6017bl">1922</a> </li><li><ms href="#un6017bl">MS TS-B</ms> </li><li>JJA 16:302 </li><li><a name="td4" href="../udra/u18da.htm#td4">Usage</a> </li><li><a href="../../ulex/t/td4.htm#un6017bl">Draft: 18.4</a></li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources">Les femmes qui les ont connus pour la premi&egrave;re fois &laquo;<mark>ces baisers lents et profonds</mark> qui semblent aspirer l&apos;&acirc;me&raquo;<sup>4</sup>, ces baisers qui de tout leur corps, pendant quelques instants, ont fait une douce et heureuse offrande d&apos;amour, elles les ont encore sur la bouche, quand celui qui les a donn&eacute;s, et commence peut-&ecirc;tre &agrave; les oublier, n&apos;est plus l&agrave;. <br><font color="green">[The women who knew them for the first time &ldquo;these slow and deep kisses that seem to suck the soul&rdquo;, these kisses which with their whole body, for a few moments, made a sweet and happy offering of love, they still have on their mouths, when the one who gave them, and perhaps begins to forget them, is no longer there.]</font> <small> Henri d'Alm&eacute;ras, <a name="HAFA" href="/udra/udex.htm#HAFA"><cite title="source">La Femme amoureuse: le C&oelig;ur et les sens</cite></a> (1920), 97</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: Footnote 4 in the source refers to &ldquo;Marcelle Tinayre. LA MAISON DU P&Eacute;CH&Eacute;&rdquo;, p.169, a novel which Joyce had reviewed for the <cite>Daily Express</cite> in 1903. </mm> </dd></dl>
